\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\qj\fi0\sb80\sa0\li0\ri0\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\scaps0\cf0 Next, we need to change the font to italic.  Select all the text inside the box (either triple-click or press-and-drag).  Type command-t to get the Font Panel (or press the \fs24\f1\b0\i0 F\f1 ont\f2\f2 ®\f1\f1 F\f1 ont Panel\f0  command, and set the font in the way usual for all NeXTStep applications.\par
